channel.title: Rune-Faction / Development Team
channel.description:
1.0 - About us
I am making a new 317 PI runescape private server. I am planning to do a lot of work on this server to make it the best. I am going to add as much features as I can to make this server stand out. __________________________________________________________________________
2.0 - My Plan
My plan is to make a very fun server. My plan is to make a server that will never be shut down. My plan is to provide a server that all people will be able to enjoy. __________________________________________________________________________
3.0 - Donation Profits
25% of our donation profits will be used on our web based interface. 75% of our donation profits will be used on server related issues we may find. I will be purchasing a custom domain name for our servers website and forums. I will be purchasing a powerful and reliable VPS for our server to be hosted on 24/7. __________________________________________________________________________
